Steps to start 

 1. npm install.
 2. node index => Your server will be running.
 3. go to 127.0.0.1:2080 to find the site.
 
 You will need a google account to set up reCAPTCHA uporn setting this up you will get 2 keys 
 a site key which goes onto the front end and a secret key which is placed on the server and used to validate requests.
 
 
 
